widgets.props:
JS{
  const props = {}
  
  const commands = [
    'cancel_stop_selectnone','keypad_/(Windows)_=(Mac)', 'keypad_*(Windows)_/(Mac)', 'keypad_-(Windows)_*(Mac)',
    'keypad7', 'keypad8', 'keypad9', 'keypad_-(Mac)',
    'keypad4', 'keypad5', 'keypad6', 'keypad_+',
    'keypad1', 'keypad2', 'keypad3', 'keypad_enter',
    'keypad0', 'keypad_.'
  ]
  
  const labels = [
    'clear','=', '/', '*',
    '7', '8', '9', '-',
    '4', '5', '6', '+',
    '1', '2', '3', 'enter',
    '0', '.'
  ]
  
  props.mode = 'tap';
  // props.linkId = '>>sibelius'
  props.on = commands[$]
  props.label = labels[$]
  props.address = '/SibeliusConnect/command'
  props.target = 'localhost:8080'
  
  if ($ === 15) props.css = 'grid-row: span 2'
  if ($ === 16) props.css = 'grid-column: span 2'
  
  return props
}
